post_summaries.description: The image is a close-up portrait of a woman dressed as Cruella Deville. She has platinum blonde hair with black streaks, styled in a blunt bob with bangs. She is wearing a white and black polka dot blouse with a red tie and a black vest. Her makeup includes bold red lipstick. The background is black.
The image shows a close-up of a vintage black jacket with intricate embellishments. The post mentions thrifting, Poshmark, Etsy, and the hashtag #fashionhacks.

The image shows a woman (thea.green) posing in a white blazer with floral decorations in the background. She is wearing statement jewelry and appears to be at a cafe or restaurant, with a small chocolate dessert in front of her.

The image shows an elaborate floral arrangement covering the ceiling and walls of what appears to be a cafe or restaurant. The flowers are mostly white and pink, with some feathery pampas grass elements. The location seems to be @brewandbloom.

The image shows a pair of long, shiny, red opera gloves that were purchased from Amazon for $9. The caption discusses a DIY project involving a glove bralette/top inspired by T.Label and mentions styling the gloves for Galentine's Day.

A close-up portrait of a woman wearing a black polka dot top, a pink bralette underneath, and multiple necklaces. She has pink gloves on. The post is tagged with fashion-related hashtags, including #diyfashion, #valentinesdayoutfit, and #lingerielove.
